author: fielding
msg: Partition RFC 2616 into seven (mostly) independent documents.
No semantic changes. Some meaningless crossreferences to prior
editorial decisions have been removed from appendices.
Structural changes minimized to simplify diff versus rfc2616.
This was a lot harder than it looks.

Updated the api-changes (from ADF 10.1.3 to Trinidad) change page to clearly identify these tags as removed.
As far as I can tell, this documentation was accidentally left over from ADF 10.1.3.
